Products.RichDescription:
Chobani FiT X No Added Sugar Low Fat Yogurt Vanilla Cookie Crush provides 13g of protein and contains chocolate cookie crunch, dark chocolate, white chocolate and cocoa soy crisps.

No added sugar, protein-packed, authentic strained Greek yogurt with a side of deliciously crunchy no added sugar mix-ins. Being good has never tasted better.

And now, you've got the chance to WIN from 25 thousand pieces of Chobani Activewear. Whether you’re at the gym, hitting up a mate's place or brunching at your local, these high quality tights or shorts will have you looking and feeling like a winner.

To WIN, simply buy any specially marked pot, peel and reveal your unique code and enter at www.chobanipromo.com.au. Specially marked packs subject to availability.

Conditions apply, see www.chobanipromo.com.au. Open to AU res. Starts 28/12/20. Ends 12:00am AEST 07/03/21. ACT Winners published on www.chobanipromo.com.au from 12/03/21. Prizes: 16,500 x Chobani fitness tights, valued at $120 each, 8,500 x Chobani fitness shorts, valued at $70 each. Promoter: Chobani PTY LTD, (ABN 53 096 731 467) of 453-455 Hammond Road, Dandenong South, Vic, 3175. Permits: NSW: LTPS/20/41457, ACT: TP20/00044, SA: T20/27.
